Paper: hep-th/9310010

Date: 1993-10-01

Title: Exact solution of the two-dimensional Dirac oscillator

Authors: Victor M. Villalba

Comments: revtex, 6pp. IVIC-CFLE 93/05

In the present article we have found the complete energy spectrum and thecorresponding eigenfunctions of the Dirac oscillator in two spatial dimensions.We show that the energy spectrum depends on the spin of the Dirac particle.